        <item>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2017-06-07T22:48:48Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Shawna Hill Post 9/11 Education Benefits Transferability Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the reassignment a veteran's or Armed Forces member's Post-9/11 education benefits to another eligible dependent in cases where the original designated beneficiary dies without having used all of such benefits.</p> <p>Such provision shall apply to deaths occurring on or after August 1, 2009.</p>]]></text>
